K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-083:457a-9: 'phags pa chos kyi rgya mtsho zhes bya ba'i gzungs rdzogs so ////
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-083:457a-10: rgya gar gyi mkhan po su randra bo dhi dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-083:457a-12: zhu chen gyi lo tsa ba bandhe ye shes sde la sogs pas bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa /
